00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:51,440
- I'm so sorry.
- Tod?

550
00:30:51,520 --> 00:30:52,960
Tod.

551
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:55,560
Tod?

552
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:12,960
Oh, you got to be kidding me. What?

553
00:31:13,040 --> 00:31:14,640
Don Maroni, you have to listen to me.

554
00:31:14,720 --> 00:31:17,640
Oh, see, no. This is how this
all began, me listening to you.

555
00:31:17,720 --> 00:31:19,680
I was telling the truth.

556
00:31:19,760 --> 00:31:22,000
About Indian Hill. And Arkham.

557
00:31:22,080 --> 00:31:25,360
Whoever controls Arkham
will control Gotham! I can...

558
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:27,800
Would you shut up and take it
like a man?

559
00:31:45,720 --> 00:31:48,200
- Yeah!
<i>- Hello, is this Mr. Duffy?</i>

560
00:31:48,280 --> 00:31:50,400
- Yeah.
<i>- Listen to me very carefully.</i>

561
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:54,040
I'm the man in the car
