687
00:41:01,320 --> 00:41:03,720
The heartless, by-the-book, hard man.

688
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:04,960
Kind of.

689
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:08,560
On the count of three,
I'm gonna lean in,

690
00:41:08,640 --> 00:41:10,600
