00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:15,320
- Come on.
- I'm serious.

693
00:41:17,200 --> 00:41:18,200
One...

694
00:41:20,040 --> 00:41:21,040
two...

695
00:41:23,360 --> 00:41:24,640
three.

696
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:44,640
